# Call hierarchy.
# Top level (called from Kurento modules, like kurento-module-core)
# |-- generate_code
# |   |-- generate_kurento_libraries
# |   |   |-- generate_sources
# |   |       |-- execute_code_generator
# |   |-- get_values_from_model
# |-- get_values_from_model
#     |-- execute_code_generator

